title: Hour 3 - Getting to the Bottom of Aaron Donald's Fight
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Getting to the Bottom of Aaron Donald's Fight
description:
La Times Rams Writer Gary Klein joins Dan Patrick to break down what sparked Aaron Donald dual wielding helmets in a training camp fight. Dan looks at some intriguing NFL and college football bets to start the season and previews Week Zero for college football.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
